content: I just spoke to a gentleman who has to change his registration to PA -- I told him it was the last day to do so and sent the text to help out. He had a lot of questions that I tried to answer, and was very anxious to make sure he got it done. Should I tag this call with a VotePro manual tag in case he needs more help?
Oh wait, I just realized that those tags are for texts. Oops! Doing too many different things for this election, lol. NVM!
Too bad we don't have something like that for Phonebanks, but they are really kinda one-way
There is a phone number is the script if it sounds like he needs more one on one help.

Unfortunately he was driving and couldn't write down the number. Hopefully the text goes through. I also repeated the website to him several times, and he repeated it back. It was nice to be able to actually help someone! Hopefully he gets it done!
